#  RecycLink Solutions

## 🌍 Project Overview
RecycLink Solutions is a smart waste management web application designed to help communities manage waste responsibly and promote environmental sustainability.

The platform allows users to:
- Track and record waste data
- Request waste collection services
- Join as waste collection lorry owners
- Learn about recycling innovations
- Visualize pollution data using charts

The system also introduces innovative environmental solutions such as:
- Recycling dirty water using treated animal dung filtration systems
- Recycling plastic waste into reusable water bottles

---

# 🚀 Problem Statement

Poor waste disposal and environmental pollution continue to affect many communities. Plastic waste, dirty water, and poor waste collection systems contribute heavily to environmental degradation.

RecycLink Solutions aims to:
- Reduce pollution
- Improve waste collection
- Encourage recycling
- Promote clean and sustainable communities

